        <section id="sector-wise-deductions">
            <h2>Sector-wise GST Rate Deductions: A Detailed Analysis</h2>

            <h3 class="mt-4">1. Consumer Electronics and Mobile Devices</h3>
            <p>The consumer electronics sector has witnessed substantial GST rate adjustments, particularly benefiting
                e-commerce platforms that dominate this market segment.</p>
            <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="table table-striped table-bordered">
                    <thead class="thead-dark">
                        <tr>
                            <th>Product Category</th>
                            <th>Previous GST Rate</th>
                            <th>Current GST Rate</th>
                            <th>Reduction</th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Mobile Phones</td>
                            <td>18%</td>
                            <td>12%</td>
                            <td>6%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Laptops & Tablets</td>
                            <td>28%</td>
                            <td>18%</td>
                            <td>10%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Smart Wearables</td>
                            <td>18%</td>
                            <td>12%</td>
                            <td>6%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>Computer Accessories</td>
                            <td>28%</td>
                            <td>18%</td>
                            <td>10%</td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td>LED TVs (up to 32")</td>
                            <td>28%</td>
                            <td>18%</td>
                            <td>10%</td>
                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
            <p><strong>Impact on E-commerce:</strong></p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Price Competitiveness:</strong> The 6-10% reduction translates directly to lower prices,
                    making online platforms more attractive</li>
                <li><strong>Increased Demand:</strong> Studies show a 25-30% increase in online electronics sales
                    post-GST reduction</li>
                <li><strong>Improved Margins:</strong> E-commerce platforms can maintain competitive prices while
                    improving profit margins</li>
                <li><strong>Market Expansion:</strong> Lower prices enable penetration into Tier-2 and Tier-3 cities
                </li>
            </ul>

